cdata.name: Ribbit Rewards
cdata.desc: RibbitRewards is the world’s first rewards program supported by block chain technology. Buyers and sellers transacting in goods and services or giving charitable donations in any currency earn RibbitRewards. No matter what currency you are transacting in, the more you buy, sell, or donate on Marketplace.Life or other participating merchant sites, the more RibbitRewards you can earn.
